一口棺材被抬到了威斯敏斯特大教堂
a coffin was carried into Westminster Abbey.

4
00:00:39,560 --> 00:00:43,200
棺材里的人曾经位高权重
In it was the body of a man who had held high office,

5
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:45,840
虽然他不是政客
although he wasn't a politician.

6
00:00:45,840 --> 00:00:49,360
